name: DMM Phantom Quickdraw
description: Super lightweight quickdraws for your trad, alpine or winter rack. 11mm Dynatec slings are super flexible so your gear is less prone to walking, and the wire gate Phantom carabiners help prevent gate flutter and keep the overall weight low.Includes 2 lightweight wire gate Phantom carabiners.Flexible and strong 11mm Dyneema sling.
